Source: sarndbox
Section: science
Priority: optional
Maintainer: SARndbox Developers <sarndbox@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10), libpng-dev, libgl-dev, libglu1-mesa-dev

Package: sarndbox
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libpng16-16, libgl1, libglu1-mesa, libusb-1.0-0
Recommends: nvidia-driver-535 | nvidia-driver-545 | nvidia-driver-550
Description: Augmented Reality Sandbox
 Projects real-time topography maps with water flow simulation
 onto a sand surface using a Kinect camera and projector.
 .
 Features include contour lines, hillshading, and animated dinosaur
 ecosystem with predator-prey dynamics.
 .
 Note: Requires Vrui 8.0 and libfreenect2 to be installed separately.
